
Types of sniffing:
- Passive sniffing
- Active sniffing
    - Mac Flooding
    - DHCP Attacks
    - DNS Poisoning
    - ARP Poisoning
    - Swtich Port Stealing
    - Spoofing Attack

Protocols vulnerable to sniffing (non encrypted protocols):
- Telnet and Rlogin
- IMAP
- HTTP
- SMTP and NNTP
- POP
- FTP

Sniffing techniques:
1. DHCP Starvation Attack (dos attack)
2. Rogue DHCP Server Attack
3. 
